Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Notes:
### - Replace {{authToken}} with your actual JWT token
### - The endpoints now use prosumer ID from the authenticated user instead of wallet address
### - The endpoints will return:
###   - 200 OK with transaction data if successful
###   - 401 Unauthorized if the token is invalid
###
